summary:
I have 7 years of experiences working with customer service. I am passionate about learning, self-motivated and results-oriented.  Through years of working with people I build up great
sensitivity to the needs of others. I have a lot of energy and I am a self-starter who is eager to get ahead in life. If a task is assigned to me I will always do what is asked of me. 
I am ready to join organization where I will have a chance to develop useful skills that would help me build my long term career goals.
I have been always loyal and dedicated to my work!
